						Electronic Menu card-ordering System


keyterms: 	Avr atmega-32,GLCD,touch-screen,Zigbee

Description:
		Here i implemented advanced menu display unit. Where GLCD will act as a menu card
		which displays all the items available in the restaurants. Touch screen will act as
		input device to take input from customer and this menu will be send via Zigbee to kitchen
		unit.
